---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 mt-auto">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- About -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-3">
          XelStack Chart
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          함수형 프로그래밍 패러다임으로 구축된 고성능 차트 라이브러리
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Links -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-3">
          Links
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li>
            <a href="/getting-started" class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-primary-600 dark:hover:text-primary-400 transition-colors">
              Documentation
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/examples" class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-primary-600 dark:hover:text-primary-400 transition-colors">
              Examples
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://github.com/xelstack/chart" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-primary-600 dark:hover:text-primary-400 transition-colors">
              GitHub
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Community -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-3">
          Community
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li>
            <a href="https://github.com/xelstack/chart/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-primary-600 dark:hover:text-primary-400 transition-colors">
              Issues
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://github.com/xelstack/chart/discussions" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-primary-600 dark:hover:text-primary-400 transition-colors">
              Discussions
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom bar -->
    <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center space-y-2 md:space-y-0">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          © {currentYear} XelStack. MIT License.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          <span>Built with Astro</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>Powered by TypeScript</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
